wildcar is a character that you use to find a specific word,file,folder, extention etc.

* represent zero or more characters
? represent a single character
[] represent a range of character

all files that start with a.
ls a* 

all the files that contain a.
ls *a*

all the files that contain a range of letters.
ls [ac]*

all the files that only has 3 characters.
ls ???
